57278465" class="weui-hidden_abs">个</span>                        </span>                                          </div>                                      <div class="article-tag__item-wrp js_tag weui-wa-hotarea js_wx_tap_highlight wx_tap_link" data-url="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/appmsgalbum?__biz=MzI2MjY2NTQ1OQ==&amp;action=getalbum&amp;album_id=3209799969566867465#wechat_redirect" data-tag_id="" data-album_id="3209799969566867465" data-tag_source="3" role="link" tabindex="0" aria-labelledby="js_article_tag_name__3209799969566867465 js_a11y_comma js_article_tag_num__3209799969566867465 js_article_tag_tips__3209799969566867465">                      <span aria-hidden="true" id="js_article_tag_name__3209799969566867465" class="article-tag__item">#缅甸</span>                                              <span aria-hidden="true" class="article-tag__item-num">                          <span id="js_article_tag_num__3209799969566867465">2</span>                          <span id="js_article_tag_tips__3209799969566867465" class="weui-hidden_abs">个</span>                        </span>                                          </div>                                      <div class="article-tag__item-wrp js_tag weui-wa-hotarea js_wx_tap_highlight wx_tap_link" data-url="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/appmsgalbum?__biz=MzI2MjY2NTQ1OQ==&amp;action=getalbum&amp;album_id=3209799970187624454#wechat_redirect" data-tag_id="" data-album_id="3209799970187624454" data-tag_source="3" role="link" tabindex="0" aria-labelledby="js_article_tag_name__3209799970187624454 js_a11y_comma js_article_tag_num__3209799970187624454 js_article_tag_tips__3209799970187624454">                      <span aria-hidden="true" id="js_article_tag_name__3209799970187624454" class="article-tag__item">#果敢</span>                                              <span aria-hidden="true" class="article-tag__item-num">                          <span id="js_article_tag_num__3209799970187624454">2</span>                          <span id="js_article_tag_tips__3209799970187624454" class="weui-hidden_abs">个</span>                        </span>                                          </div>                                                </div>                      </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 0em;">缅甸的局势是越来越恶化了！</span><br></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;">除了果敢同盟军在果敢老街攻城拔寨，将支持电诈的五大家族打得灰飞烟灭之时，位于缅甸南部的克伦武装联盟也突然开始起兵，宣布向另一个电诈大本营妙瓦底KK园区发起行动，一时间，缅甸敏昂莱政府变得风雨飘摇起来。</span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;">但是靠军事政变软禁昂山素季上台的敏昂莱也不是等闲之辈，尤其是手里还握几十万大军，怎么肯就此善罢甘休。</span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;">在多次派兵支援果敢被同盟军打败之后，敏昂莱恼羞成怒，宣布将对缅北武装发起大规模的空袭行动。</span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100029381" data-ratio="0.698159509202454" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lh06VCd95btnXXggYP42FneLI4GrmBy3DThCadabvDEK6bpzkJLnedKj2pTZBgk0vTCCRAW7ScWFiaXYNyqoptA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="815"></span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;">没错，这是眼看地面支援部队打不过果敢同盟军，这是要动用空中部队来打击果敢同盟军了。</span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;">要知道，果敢老街还有大量的华人华侨以及外国人没有彻底撤离，如果缅甸军政府对果敢老街采取无差别轰炸的话，必将造成大量人员伤亡，同时也会在缅甸北部造成大量难民潮涌向中国边界，给中国的边境管理带来压力。</span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;">上一次缅北武装和缅甸军政府交战之时，就造成大量缅北难民涌向中国境内，并且由炮弹落入中国境内，造成中国老百姓的伤亡。</span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;">而这一次双方交战的规模更大，使用的火力和重型武器也会更多，如果果敢大决战打响，尤其是缅甸军政府对果敢采取大规模轰炸的话，造成重大人员伤亡是在所难免，势必有更大规模的难民潮涌向中国云南。</span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100029384" data-ratio="0.6546666666666666" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lh06VCd95btnXXggYP42FneLI4GrmBy3Udib0Ed5Vialuv906RwhnHsTibaJ5SteRQ7eNvtga928JfvqTrnFfJ2nA/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="other" data-w="750"></span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;">而恰在此时，就在中缅边境金三角地带，缅甸一大型中转物流基地遭到大规模轰炸，数百辆中国制造的货车也在这次轰炸当中付之一炬。</span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;">对于这次轰物流基地，果敢同盟军以及缅甸军政府都指责是对方发动了袭击行动，但由此也证明，战火正在一步步烧向中国边境，局势也变得越来越危险了。</span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;">就在缅甸军政府宣布将要大规模空袭缅北果敢同盟军之时，昨天，解放军突然宣布一条重磅消息，解放军已经在中缅边境开展大规模实战演习。</span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;">你没看错，解放军迅即出兵了！</span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-croporisrc="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lh06VCd95btnXXggYP42FneLI4GrmBy3WsVIghzm3eMAsuQXDWH9iam4LEeXhTN3a1icNibib3jVTr5r7QPSYyIZYw/0?wx_fmt=other&amp;from=appmsg" data-cropx1="0" data-cropx2="1073" data-cropy1="0" data-cropy2="605.1868512110727" data-imgfileid="100029390" data-ratio="0.5629077353215284" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lh06VCd95btnXXggYP42FneLI4GrmBy3BqTd95kBMMhLBFcqyu7SHoEtk0IQ4bRCPxb90VpVdujfFzY9XsFaTg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1073" style="width: 578px;height: 326px;"></span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;">就在缅甸双方大决战即将打响，缅甸军政府威胁要大轰炸之时，解放军迅即出兵了，并且是直接在中缅边境展开了大规模的实战演习。</span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;">对于缅甸交战双方来说，这条消息都无疑是一条炸雷！</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 0em;"></span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;">很明显，这就是在公开警告缅甸交战双方，无论是谁，.都不要损害中国利益！也不要妄想把中国拖下水，要不然，我手里的家伙不答应！</span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-croporisrc="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lh06VCd95btnXXggYP42FneLI4GrmBy38ibqABfaqibwRu37AjoWv3oP5ibx8npz6bm76p8oVa5Ecs97evYEFZn7w/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-cropx1="0" data-cropx2="1080" data-cropy1="0" data-cropy2="726.8512110726643" data-imgfileid="100029387" data-ratio="0.6722222222222223" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lh06VCd95btnXXggYP42FneLI4GrmBy3b8PM1W8I3r2S8kSX0gYJWjkxY3Qg5tPmIb9J2eqFLia8BOrXZJC5iaRw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="height: 389px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;white-space: normal;width: 578px;"></span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;">对于中国方面突然发起的大规模实战演习，并且是紧靠中缅边境，相信这个信号，缅甸军政府以及果敢同盟军都能感受得到。</span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;">所以他们在接下来的行动当中，都必将有所顾忌，尤其是缅甸军政府，在缅北实施大规模轰炸之前，就更要考虑后果了！</span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;">不要忘了，就在前几天缅甸军政府动用直升机对果敢同盟军发动空袭的时候就被果敢同盟军直接击落了。</span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;">如果缅甸军政府不顾及后果，执意对果敢展开大规模轰炸行动，造成大量难民涌入中国境内，那么果敢同盟军在深山老林里面突然捡到防空武器也说不定了！</span></section><section class="mp_profile_iframe_wrp"><mp-common-profile class="js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe" data-pluginname="mpprofile" data-id="MzIzNTgxMjI5MA==" data-headimg="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/839TU4qkibmtNlLr8QSZevqzFkxniaKLW4r1QQ5BMlRBKGoYspXKYxqKgia1qlReJ4GTVYHFoaxg7b4Pq1ykNichZw/0?wx_fmt=png" data-nickname="大嘴犀评" data-alias="jujiao1166" data-signature="评说热点内幕  关注百姓民生" data-from="0" data-is_biz_ban="0"></mp-common-profile></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none;"><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2MjY2NTQ1OQ==&amp;mid=2247513027&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=c94aa8c4711a6ef88977465c73837c9a&amp;chksm=ea45565fdd32df492e6a6c56f49621d6480af24b3384e9ffa40afc32c553b3f2a4e11ceab7dd&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="缅甸突发，彻底变天了！" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="2">缅甸突发，彻底变天了！</a></span></section><section style="line-height: 1.6em;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-indent: 0em;"><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2MjY2NTQ1OQ==&amp;mid=2247513017&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=e890189dd7139ffadf1d029e4d526af3&amp;chksm=ea455625dd32df33326f94bdb0b88e5a4dd73d757f04d85705bbfa034ff244aa11555e312b5b&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="台湾突发！郭台铭终于怕了！" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="2">台湾突发！郭台铭终于怕了！</a></section><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="2016998358" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display